  <dsc><c01 id="aspace_ea5d4c6aacfb8a5816bbbffda271da40" level="file"><did><unittitle>Periodicals and news clippings</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1979/1979">1979</unitdate><unitdate normal="1984/1992" type="inclusive">1984-1992</unitdate><container id="aspace_8bf68a681c039dc3452ed5bf11d81a15" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_d6e31175fc9900fa0d93f11bab155bf1" parent="aspace_8bf68a681c039dc3452ed5bf11d81a15" type="folder">1</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_46a41258357d2dae29d06ca6db632e71"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Includes debate over gay priests, potential cause of AIDS identified.</p></scopecontent></c01><c01 id="aspace_a28f7faa1d58b96d1359f367dc6e5104" level="file"><did><unittitle>Promotional materials</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1987/1991" type="inclusive">1987-1991</unitdate><unitdate normal="1994/1994">1994</unitdate><container id="aspace_a7609d19dafdbf09f2ae6c637fa072ff" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_7cab2c8dae04516898045590720b0478" parent="aspace_a7609d19dafdbf09f2ae6c637fa072ff" type="folder">2</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_e4659220f8c2aa2c0b247e6d587d6998"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Fliers, pamphlets, programs, invitations for conventions, events, resorts in and around Rochester.</p></scopecontent></c01><c01 id="aspace_33d896b8ae762019aef74f6b03c58294" level="file"><did><unittitle>"Is the Church Today a Dysfunctional Family?: A Pastoral Letter from Matthew Fox to Cardinal Ratzinger"</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1988-08-08/1988-08-08">August 8, 1988</unitdate><container id="aspace_cf58dbcc9c5a196aebaf51c117bce8aa" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_09a6c6c3db49d8576f6fb00319c8f5bc" parent="aspace_cf58dbcc9c5a196aebaf51c117bce8aa" type="folder">3</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_a802fde11fdd9bb448b83453c7c1e750"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>An article of a letter from Matthew Fox, O.P., writing to Cardinal Ratzinger and the whole Church, defending his work against Ratzinger's criticisms that it is unorthodox, dangerous, and deviant.</p></scopecontent></c01><c01 id="aspace_9738d5a12a087b5bfc68a58515569a46" level="file"><did><unittitle>Bias-Related Violence Bill- Debate Transcript</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1990-09-13/1990-09-13">September 13, 1990</unitdate><container id="aspace_0b3d4b5529a3a11d57a581872e2a02b3" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_8e80ea43029deabf7773121f369a5c79" parent="aspace_0b3d4b5529a3a11d57a581872e2a02b3" type="folder">4</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_d043d77309cf254a79f5abf8b0f61e56" level="file"><did><unittitle>Letter from the Diocese of Rochester</unittitle><unitdate calendar="gregorian" era="ce" normal="1997-03-13/1997-03-13">March 13, 1997</unitdate><container id="aspace_5531a898d3c94ce6fa0a03638d36158e" label="Mixed Materials [31924088321983]" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_6c0ebe8634a4947ef1aef887b62d340c" parent="aspace_5531a898d3c94ce6fa0a03638d36158e" type="folder">5</container></did><scopecontent id="aspace_b9f6021978790c9ad3e79df1a1a7a331"><head>Scope and Contents</head><p>Letter from Matthew Clark, Bishop of Rochester, thanking Mary McCrank for her support of their celebration for gay and lesbian Catholics.</p></scopecontent></c01></dsc>
